{"word":"ἐγκαρτερέω","slug":"ἐγκαρτερέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐγκαρτερέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to persevere</i> or <i>persist in</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to await stedfastly</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to hold out, remain firm</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}